Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===========PART1===========
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.57,0:01:37.16,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔境转生！达令你在想些什么！？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.34,0:02:01.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是炫目之海
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.28,0:02:03.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么那么美
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.18,0:02:05.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像我的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.15,0:02:07.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿忍的眼睛是黑的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.86,0:02:10.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对在我眼睛还黑亮之时
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.86,0:02:13.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会让人碰面堂的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.44,0:02:19.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是为何要坐这种旧型破烂螺旋桨飞机
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.80,0:02:20.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么叫破烂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.14,0:02:23.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这B-29是我秘密的收藏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.87,0:02:25.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能让你坐就该感谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.94,0:02:29.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果叫收破烂的来收的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.39,0:02:32.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少可换卫生纸二 三十包
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.20,0:02:33.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诸星
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.05,0:02:36.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以在这里下机哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.24,0:02:39.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,B-29真是棒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.09,0:02:43.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这外观之美真…是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.13,0:02:45.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透过粗俗的墙壁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.88,0:02:50.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像感觉到英勇之空中男儿活生生的气息
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.71,0:02:56.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诸星 好好听着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.25,0:02:58.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本计划在旧历新年
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.18,0:03:02.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我面堂财阀新开发南方乐园
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.33,0:03:04.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥克斯帕乐园度过
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.86,0:03:08.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来是只有我和拉姆小姐 阿忍小姐的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.52,0:03:32.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你却缠…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.57,0:03:36.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带我去嘛…这么的拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.24,0:03:38.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有拉姆小姐的缘故 没办法之下才…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.11,0:04:01.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白的说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.03,0:04:04.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对我而言是累赘
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.78,0:04:06.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有比这更讨厌了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.14,0:04:09.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.77,0:04:12.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.06,0:04:13.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.75,0:04:14.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.81,0:04:17.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为燃料没有了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.68,0:04:21.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此时累赘越少越好…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.18,0:04:22.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.68,0:04:27.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.05,0:04:29.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面堂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.02,0:04:48.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先动的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.72,0:04:50.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会倒…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.93,0:04:57.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些家伙不可原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.36,0:04:59.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然将主人的我踢开
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.85,0:05:01.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去要受鞭刑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.09,0:05:17.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看样子是不必了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.01,0:05:18.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是岛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.80,0:05:38.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先动的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.40,0:05:41.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会倒…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.17,0:05:52.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.93,0:05:54.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是无人岛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.17,0:05:57.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面堂 你要怎么负责呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.54,0:05:59.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别装蒜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.55,0:06:02.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会如此 全都是你对部下教育不当之故
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.75,0:06:05.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面堂 如果你是男人就在此切腹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.39,0:06:09.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 对我出此豪语行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.60,0:06:13.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用这联络一下 救援队马上就来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.91,0:06:16.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是面堂 准备得很充分
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.74,0:06:18.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小终 鞋子脏了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.16,0:06:22.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你切腹的话 也没什么不可原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.00,0:06:26.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肩膀酸了吗？我最会按摩了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.21,0:06:27.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.14,0:06:30.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此后可别忘了那可怜的态度
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.79,0:06:33.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是终太郎 终太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.77,0:06:35.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面堂邸第一控制中心请回答
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.13,0:06:40.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 听不见吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.62,0:06:41.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一控制中心回答
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.21,0:06:46.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪 是不是故障了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.19,0:07:00.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切腹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.83,0:07:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切腹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.26,0:07:08.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.78,0:07:23.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.10,0:07:25.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.15,0:07:27.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许能得救
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.08,0:07:31.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.48,0:07:34.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像说“不要”？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.91,0:07:38.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不要 不要就是要嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.18,0:07:52.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.91,0:08:03.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 拉姆 你误会了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.99,0:08:06.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 不要 面堂怎么可以
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.96,0:08:08.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静 阿忍小姐 冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.24,0:08:11.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们只是想问个路
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.27,0:08:13.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.30,0:08:33.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅途中发生事故啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.78,0:08:35.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真是辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.85,0:08:47.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小杏 替客人准备饭菜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.90,0:08:57.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爷爷 请将小杏交付给我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.71,0:08:59.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.81,0:09:05.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要出这岛 用船 或是飞机
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.98,0:09:07.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没有那些东西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.69,0:09:13.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这村子是极力避免外界之交流
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.09,0:09:17.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将日本人古来的纯粹之心顽固地保存着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.10,0:09:19.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孙女的小杏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.77,0:09:21.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见到村外之人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.13,0:09:24.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想你们可是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.73,0:09:26.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.84,0:09:28.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才那么恐慌
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.02,0:09:31.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.17,0:09:36.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我居然在不知污秽之纯洁少女心\N划上了不能抹灭的伤痕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.48,0:09:40.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爷爷 我负责这个责任
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.96,0:09:43.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会用一生照顾小杏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.22,0:09:45.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会变这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.11,0:09:51.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿忍小姐 怎么了呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.01,0:09:56.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为 我们无法离开这岛嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.55,0:09:58.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有在此生活了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.70,0:10:00.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.94,0:10:02.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有我在嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.50,0:10:04.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面堂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.20,0:10:12.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 既然你如此希望
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.55,0:10:14.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就和你结为夫妻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.07,0:10:16.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这岛上过着虽然平凡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.34,0:10:18.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但幸福的日子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.35,0:10:21.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子要男孩女孩各一个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.28,0:10:23.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然绝不用奶粉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.83,0:10:36.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.92,0:10:38.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毒菇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.72,0:10:40.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而将这如何处理
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.01,0:10:42.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放入口内
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.22,0:10:45.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,充分咬碎后放入胃内
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.90,0:10:47.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说叫我们吃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.83,0:10:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安心吧 这种菇是蕈伞上有毒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.66,0:10:56.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个则在枝上有毒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.51,0:10:59.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如各位所见 有毒之处全拿走了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.45,0:11:13.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.12,0:11:15.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杏小姐 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.04,0:11:29.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是竹笋
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.56,0:00:02.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===========PART2===========
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.55,0:12:18.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.53,0:12:21.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前阵子死去的娟婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.26,0:12:23.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢在中午吃竹笋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.85,0:12:26.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以生来的就是竹笋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.81,0:12:28.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.68,0:12:41.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了 小杏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.83,0:12:43.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.15,0:13:00.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是长老
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.26,0:13:13.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长老那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.22,0:13:16.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.67,0:13:33.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天到这时候会来买竹笋的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.65,0:13:37.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说用于奥克帕斯岛旅馆的料理
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.83,0:13:39.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 奥克帕斯岛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.75,0:13:40.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.21,0:13:41.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.00,0:13:44.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我 面堂终太郎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.74,0:13:45.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.22,0:13:48.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是面堂家后继者 面堂终太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.99,0:13:50.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.76,0:13:51.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.96,0:13:53.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我 面堂终太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.91,0:13:57.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后继人的面堂终…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.63,0:14:04.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村民们 不得了了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.89,0:14:07.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,权太家的佐助爷爷吃了中毒了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.96,0:14:08.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.89,0:14:47.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.79,0:14:55.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这 这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.49,0:14:57.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.31,0:15:05.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.56,0:15:08.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助爷爷最喜欢武打了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.78,0:15:17.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二刀流 宫本武藏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.70,0:15:20.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岩流 佐佐木小次郎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.20,0:15:22.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小次郎 你输了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.61,0:15:23.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.68,0:15:28.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丢弃了刀 要如何赢我武藏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.74,0:15:29.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.25,0:15:39.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 牛若
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.25,0:15:42.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.41,0:15:48.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由这村子取得的东西全部含毒的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.01,0:15:50.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃下毒之人的思想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.07,0:15:52.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便以实际状态出现
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.07,0:15:54.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是这么回事而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.61,0:15:58.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.09,0:15:58.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.02,0:16:01.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不能一直在此晃荡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.02,0:16:02.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.74,0:16:05.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小杏 我们也走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.37,0:17:07.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次又是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.49,0:17:25.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕 面堂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.38,0:17:27.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会有事的 阿忍小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.06,0:17:29.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有我在你身边嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.00,0:17:36.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.78,0:17:39.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.06,0:17:40.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.75,0:17:43.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.46,0:17:48.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.86,0:17:49.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.63,0:17:59.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加速装置
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.07,0:18:07.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.46,0:18:08.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脸色不太好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.54,0:18:12.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有怪…物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.73,0:18:15.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.69,0:18:17.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我是人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.78,0:18:19.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想也是 看就晓得了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.24,0:18:21.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪…物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.86,0:18:24.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真无礼 我是人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.57,0:18:36.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.61,0:18:39.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小杏确实喜欢古怪的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.53,0:18:40.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.47,0:18:41.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.03,0:18:46.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小杏 怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.25,0:18:50.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么能这么镇定
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.64,0:18:52.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杏小姐是您孙女啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.10,0:18:57.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一个人吃了毒 阿杏就会复活
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.26,0:19:04.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在佐助爷爷也复活了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.05,0:19:11.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次是谁吃了毒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.58,0:19:13.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看样子…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.19,0:19:16.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是小杏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.93,0:19:21.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 你们也必须遵从村里的规定
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.18,0:19:24.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村…规定
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.10,0:19:25.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.26,0:19:28.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,踏入此村庄之人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.89,0:19:30.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每个人都得做试毒人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.91,0:19:33.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为大家的食物安全贡献
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.56,0:19:37.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,权太家是专尝鱼类的试毒店
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.58,0:19:40.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隔壁的仁兵卫则是鸟肉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.22,0:19:41.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家是菇类
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.93,0:19:43.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在长久的岁月间
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.88,0:19:47.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们祖先一直先尝新的毒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.34,0:19:49.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而找出安全的食物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.94,0:19:50.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.88,0:19:53.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也必须尝许多东西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.58,0:19:56.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找出无毒之部分才行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.87,0:19:59.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放在各位面前的是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.20,0:20:02.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未经品尝的新品种毒菇
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.53,0:20:07.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么 吃了马上就能活了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.54,0:20:13.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对地球人是毒 对我一定没用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.68,0:20:16.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这是这村庄的规矩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.81,0:20:17.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不能不知
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.18,0:20:20.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有义即有勇…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.56,0:20:23.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知这个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.08,0:20:26.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就无法在此生活
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.34,0:20:29.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了和面堂的新生活
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.30,0:20:39.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.50,0:20:42.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿当
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.53,0:20:43.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诸星
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.48,0:20:44.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.19,0:20:54.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.85,0:21:20.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这世界变得真好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.01,0:21:22.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.19,0:21:32.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是汗颜的是世界
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.72,0:21:35.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面堂 还是不要靠得太近
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.44,0:21:42.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.44,0:21:43.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.73,0:21:46.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真开朗的鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.44,0:21:49.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我叫开心鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.74,0:21:52.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有点像达令
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.68,0:21:55.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.93,0:21:58.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是叫无节操之草
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.08,0:22:06.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是思迁树…马上就会走了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.26,0:22:09.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿当那小子到底想些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.38,0:22:14.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 是起关马
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.36,0:22:16.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是极乐蜻蜓
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.08,0:22:20.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而那是今日蝉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.04,0:22:24.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何 为何要受此待遇地吃菇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.52,0:22:26.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.78,0:22:31.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要建立文化 要有非常之努力及忍耐才行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.92,0:22:34.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这汗颜的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.82,0:22:36.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是为此之布石
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.71,0:22:40.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文化 文化 只是多一种菇吃嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.01,0:22:43.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是文化
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.18,0:22:51.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面堂 不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.88,0:22:53.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小哥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.10,0:22:57.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是杏小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.39,0:23:15.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看样子正如气象队的报告
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.50,0:23:17.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往这村庄再也不能取竹笋了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.06,0:23:20.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想也不会再到这村庄了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.09,0:23:27.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受毒侵害的痛苦中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.88,0:23:29.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父母对孩子说
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.96,0:23:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这红菇的红色蒂是不可以吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.67,0:23:37.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但味道可绝不能忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.01,0:23:39.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后传至那孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.99,0:23:41.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后再传至其子孙
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.37,0:23:45.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不断地持续之命运
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.56,0:00:02.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===========预告===========
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.23,0:23:51.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友引町正是冬天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.80,0:23:54.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在面堂家的巨大温室中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.32,0:23:56.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二年四班正集合赏花中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.29,0:23:59.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我从幽浮带来的果汁之中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.26,0:24:01.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有标识着不得了的注意事项
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.67,0:24:02.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.37,0:24:05.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演戏大乱弄！面堂家赏花宴
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.54,0:24:06.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.56,0:00:02.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===========OP===========
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.29,0:00:10.45,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宝贝 我能说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.94,0:00:13.62,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的感触是否能传达
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.15,0:00:16.19,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想在你身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.20,0:00:18.09,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你愿意爱我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.10,0:00:23.65,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们取得爱的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.66,0:00:36.20,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被你的手所拥在怀里 在耳边轻声细语
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.28,0:00:50.53,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远都不要离开我 我会给你个甜美的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.44,0:00:55.56,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请感受我 请了解我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.92,0:00:59.61,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将我揽在你的臂弯里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.09,0:01:03.35,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你对我轻轻地微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.35,0:01:06.77,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我将日日夜夜爱着你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.87,0:01:12.50,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无人比我更爱着你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.50,0:01:15.72,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的爱是如此真诚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.17,0:01:17.93,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想在你身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.94,0:01:20.06,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是否爱我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.06,0:01:25.39,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们取得爱的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.56,0:00:02.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===========ED===========
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.94,0:24:30.56,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将银轮偷偷交给你 这是只有你一人的邀请函
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.67,0:24:36.37,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我尝试保有它 是我小小的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.37,0:24:41.91,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约定在今日 只有两人的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.15,0:24:49.58,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是公开的邀请
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.13,0:24:53.49,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我将准备庆贺
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.01,0:24:56.98,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦！宝贝 给你个讯息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.71,0:25:01.26,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我将献上所有的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.70,0:25:05.18,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是我的想象
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.67,0:25:09.10,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你早些感受我
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.59,0:25:12.72,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来！给我些诱惑
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.35,0:25:16.94,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的要我如此吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.43,0:25:20.05,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请常来看我
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.05,0:25:23.18,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我将表示我的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.22,0:25:27.86,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当我和你在一起时
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.86,0:25:31.03,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是如何的美好

